text: Renan Andrade Ferreira (born 31 May 1995), or simply Renan, is a Brazilian footballer who plays as a defender for Tulsa Roughnecks in the USL Championship. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:Brazilian footballers Category:FC Tulsa players Category:USL Championship players
